SUMMARY:⛰️ 🛫 PERU ADVENTURE: INCA TRAIL Trek to Machu Picchu (8 Days): May 9-16\, 2026
DESCRIPTION:Hiking Network\n⭐️ AN INCREDIBLE HIKING & CAMPING ADVENTURE IN THE PERUVIAN ANDES FROM CUSCO TO MACHU PICCHU ⭐️\n(Includes all camping supplies and round-trip flight Lima-Cusco)\n\n**May 9–16\, 2026** • 8 Days / 7 Nights\n\n**Difficulty level:** **Intermediate** (recent experience hiking 14 Km (8.7 mi) a day or more required).\n\n**Max 16 participants**\n\n⭐️⭐️ PRICE: CAD **$3\,350**\n\n**• HIGHLIGHTS**\nExperience the thrill of a lifetime with this hiking adventure in one of the world's most iconic destinations for outdoor and culture enthusiasts – Peru’s ancient **Inca Trail** to **Machu Picchu**\, a UNESCO World Heritage Site.\nJoin us on this fully escorted and guided tour of spectacular **Peru** and retrace the steps of the Incas – Peru's fascinating ancient civilization. Beginning in **Lima**\, the country’s capital flanked by Spanish colonial architecture\, you’ll journey through the fertile heartland of the **Sacred Valley**\, see the magnificent **Ollantaytambo** ruins and take on the world-renowned Inca Trail to Machu Picchu – nestled high in the **Andes**\, this is one of the Seven Wonders of the World… AND MORE!\n\n**• ITINERARY**\nVISIT [https://intrepid.wetravel.com/i/68704a47d4f8f8b11938b4e6](https://intrepid.wetravel.com/i/68704a47d4f8f8b11938b4e6)\n\n⭐️ ⭐️ HOW TO REGISTER ⭐️ ⭐️\n**[>> Please\, Click HERE <<](https://intrepid.wetravel.com/i/68704a47d4f8f8b11938b4e6)**[ ](https://intrepid.wetravel.com/i/68704a47d4f8f8b11938b4e6)to see the full description and register via **Intrepid Travel\,** Canada (TICO Reg. **N. 50020269**)\n\n⭐️ Event offered in conjunction with via Intrepid Travel\, a global leader in small-group experiential tours\, est. in 1989 ([IntrepidTravel.com](http://intrepidtravel.com/)) ⭐️
